00:14:59,431 --> 00:15:00,599
Mr. Do.

226
00:15:01,267 --> 00:15:04,670
We get two new pairs
of slippers every day.

227
00:15:05,404 --> 00:15:08,941
I need new ones every other day,

228
00:15:09,041 --> 00:15:10,876
so can I take the rest?

229
00:15:11,243 --> 00:15:12,444
Thank you.

230
00:15:33,732 --> 00:15:36,001
We spent way too much time together.

231
00:15:49,949 --> 00:15:53,352
Of course I love the hotel buffet
even more than myself.

232
