But it's not like

233
00:15:55,354 --> 00:15:57,856
I can't let you eat there
every single day.

234
00:15:58,324 --> 00:15:59,825
I'll cook

235
00:15:59,892 --> 00:16:02,261
at least one meal a day for you.

236
00:16:03,896 --> 00:16:05,564
"At first,

237
00:16:06,632 --> 00:16:09,468
I thought she talked too much."

