BOSS

239
00:16:35,027 --> 00:16:36,729
Hello.

240
00:16:37,596 --> 00:16:38,731
Are you sleeping?

241
00:16:39,498 --> 00:16:41,266
Yes.

242
00:16:42,634 --> 00:16:43,936
