Did you forget it?

246
00:16:52,945 --> 00:16:54,813
I'm sorry.

247
00:16:56,081 --> 00:16:58,617
I got home safely.

248
00:16:59,885 --> 00:17:00,719
All right then.

249
00:17:00,786 --> 00:17:03,622
I can't sleep
because of the stockholders' meeting.

250
00:17:03,956 --> 00:17:06,358
And my secretary is sleeping just fine?

251
00:17:06,859 --> 00:17:08,360
Is it what a secretary would do

252
00:17:08,427 --> 00:17:09,995
to help her boss become the CEO?

253
00:17:10,362 --> 00:17:12,197
I must say

254
00:17:12,264 --> 00:17:14,500
you have no respect for your boss.

255
00:17:14,566 --> 00:17:16,435
It's like the tail wagging the dog.

256
00:17:16,502 --> 00:17:18,337
What did you say?

257
00:17:21,173 --> 00:17:23,075
You're the one who sent me home.

258
00:17:23,308 --> 00:17:26,678
And it's not my fault
that you can't fall asleep.

259
00:17:26,845 --> 00:17:27,813
Why don't you

260
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:30,049
blame me for your constipation?

261
00:17:30,115 --> 00:17:33,018
I don't have constipation.
That's disgusting.

262
00:17:34,353 --> 00:17:36,789
I could tell
while we spent a few days together.

263
00:17:37,689 --> 00:17:40,259
