265
00:17:41,427 --> 00:17:43,062
for at least 30 minutes with your phone.

266
00:17:43,495 --> 00:17:45,197
Do you even know

267
00:17:45,264 --> 00:17:48,033
that I look haggard
because of bad smell, not overwork?

268
